| schedpolicy      | None                                 |
| txhashpolicy     | None                                 |
| uuid             | 8ca9854e-a18e-4a3c-8afe-f050da702fdf |
| ihost_uuid       | 3d207384-7d30-4bc0-affe-d68ab6a00a5b |
| vlan_id          | 22                                   |
| uses             | [u'eth1']                            |
